# Environment Variables — Client

Copy this file to `.env.local` before running the development server.
`.env.local` is excluded from version control via `.gitignore`.

# ─── API ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Base URL for the REST API.
# Leave blank (or as-is) to use local mock data.
# Change to your backend URL when one is available.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000/api

# ─── Feature flags ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Set to 'false' to route data requests to the real API instead of mock data.
VITE_USE_MOCK_DATA=true
